# .claudeignore

# -----------------------------------------------------------
# OpenTofu / Terraform Specific
# -----------------------------------------------------------
# Ignore the massive downloaded provider binaries and local modules
.terraform/

# Ignore state files (CRITICAL FOR SECURITY AND COST)
# State files contain massive JSON structures and plaintext secrets.
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfstate.backup

# Ignore crash logs
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Ignore variables files that might contain local AWS credentials or DB passwords
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
# Note: If you have a 'terraform.tfvars.example' or 'non-sensitive.tfvars',
# you can explicitly un-ignore them if you want the AI to read your variable structures.

# Ignore plan output files (binary files generated by `tofu plan -out=plan.tfplan`)
*.tfplan
*.plan

# -----------------------------------------------------------
# General DevOps & IDE Noise
# -----------------------------------------------------------
.git/
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
*.pem
*.key
